OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,FWhile Andy Burnham is still the
OL,7,Ffavourite to become the next PM,
OL,8,Fquestions remain over his policy
OL,9,Fpositions and what exactly qualifies
OL,10,Fhim for the job. ITV News' Rachel
OL,11,FTownsend explains
OL,13,FAdditional reporting by Nations and
OL,14,FRegions News Editor, Jade Liversidge
OL,16,FEvery day brings more certainty that
OL,17,FAndy Burnham will become Prime
OL,18,FMinister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
