OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,FThe former Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,7,F- now Makerfield MP - met Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer today, prompting renewed
OL,9,Fdiscussion about his future ambitions.
OL,11,FBut alongside questions about Burnham
OL,12,Fhimself, attention is increasingly
OL,13,Fturning to the political philosophy
OL,14,Fthat has defined his decade in office
OL,15,F` a model that supporters have dubbed
OL,16,F"Manchesterism".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
