OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,FThe term refers to Burnham's belief
OL,7,Fthat economic growth, public services
OL,8,Fand political power should be driven
OL,9,Ffrom cities and regions, rather than
OL,10,Ffrom Westminster.
OL,12,FAt its heart is a simple argument:
OL,13,Flocal leaders understand local
OL,14,Fproblems better than central
OL,15,Fgovernment and should therefore have
OL,16,Fgreater control over transport,
OL,17,Fhousing, skills and investment.
OL,19,FFor Burnham's allies, Manchesterism is
OL,20,Fmore than a slogan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
