OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782290901
OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,FThey point to Greater Manchester's
OL,7,Fgrowing powers, the expansion of the
OL,8,FBee Network transport system and
OL,9,Fefforts to tackle homelessness and
OL,10,Fhousing inequality as evidence that
OL,11,Fdevolved government can deliver
OL,12,Ftangible results.
OL,14,FHis former deputy mayor, Sir Richard
OL,15,FLeese, described Manchesterism as a
OL,16,Fframework in which growth is driven
OL,17,Flocally, and communities have greater
OL,18,Fcontrol over the decisions that affect
OL,19,Ftheir lives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
