OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782290901
OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,F"He won't be saying, devolve power
OL,7,Fthis way, these are the powers, this
OL,8,Fis what you need to do for your
OL,9,Fpeople", Sir Leese said.
OL,11,FAdding: "He'll say make it work for
OL,12,Fthe place where you live. And that's
OL,13,Fthe important thing about Manchester-
OL,14,Fism. It was designed for Manchester,
OL,15,Fbut the principles behind it are
OL,16,Fapplicable everywhere."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
