OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,FBurnham's profile rose significantly
OL,7,Fduring the Covid pandemic, when he
OL,8,Fpublicly challenged Boris Johnson's
OL,9,Fgovernment over financial support for
OL,10,Fareas facing local restrictions.
OL,12,FHis refusal to accept Westminster's
OL,13,Ffunding offer helped build him into a
OL,14,Fnational figure and, for many
OL,15,Fsupporters, demonstrated the core
OL,16,Fprinciples of Manchesterism in action:
OL,17,Fstanding up for local interests
OL,18,Fagainst central government.
OL,20,FThe moment helped cement Burnham's
OL,21,Freputation beyond Greater Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
