OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,FInspired by his anger, local artist
OL,7,FStanley Chow created a portrait
OL,8,Fdepicting him as an anti-establishment
OL,9,Ffigure.
OL,11,FThe image became synonymous with
OL,12,FBurnham's political identity and later
OL,13,Ffeatured prominently in his successful
OL,14,Fcampaign to return to Parliament.
OL,16,F"I think it's because it's different,"
OL,17,FChow said of the portrait. "Barack
OL,18,FObama had one similar when he became
OL,19,FPresident but that's it. And it
OL,20,Fhumanises him, shows he is not a robot
OL,21,Fbut a man of the people."
OL,26,@}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
