OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,F"I've met him a few times now - I'd
OL,7,Fdefinitely go for a pint with him",
OL,8,Fthe artist added.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FBurnham's advocacy for affordable
OL,16,Fhousing, universal social care and
OL,17,Fpublicly controlled transport has
OL,18,Fearned him widespread support in
OL,19,FGreater Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
