OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782290901
OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,FYet the question facing both the
OL,7,Fpolitician and his political
OL,8,Fphilosophy is whether success in one
OL,9,Fregion can be replicated across the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FLiam Thorp, political editor at the
OL,13,FLiverpool Echo, who co-authored
OL,14,FBurnham's book, Heading North,
OL,15,Fbelieves that remains the great
OL,16,Funknown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
