OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782290901
OL,3,CManchesterism: How Andy Burnham built
OL,4,Ca political movement beyond Westminster
OL,6,F"It's a completely different ball
OL,7,Fgame," he said. "The hardest job in
OL,8,Fthe country requires decisions that
OL,9,Fupset people every day. That's the big
OL,10,Ftest for Andy Burnham."
OL,12,FFor now, Manchesterism remains a
OL,13,Fdistinctly regional political project.
OL,14,FBut as Burnham's national profile
OL,15,Fgrows, so too does interest in whether
OL,16,Fthe model could provide a blueprint
OL,17,Ffor Labour's future ` and perhaps one
OL,18,Fday very soon - a route to Downing
OL,19,FStreet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
